      *最終工程*
     C                     MOVELJ6ATOK    STOK    3
      *収容数*
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     SYOS    50
     C                     Z-ADDJ6SYOS    SYOS
      *
     C                     SETON                     U1
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       PHAK
     C                     Z-ADDJ6SYOS    WSYOS   50
      *箱種がＧの時、１箱重量に焼入れロット箱数をかける。
      * J6HKJR 3(1)が桁数不足なので、N@HKJR 4(1)を追加
      *
     C                     Z-ADDJ6HKJR    N@HKJR  41
     C                     Z-ADD0         W@HKJR  72
      *
S1   C           J6SYOT    IFEQ 'G'
      *
 S2  C           J6SOZI    IFNE 0
     C           J6SOZI    MULT J6SYOS    W1HK    71H
     C           W1HK      DIV  1000      W@HKJR
     C           W@HKJR    ADD  .09       N@HKJR
 E2  C                     END
      *
 S2  C* * *      J6LOTO    IFNE 0
     C* * *      N@HKJR    MULT J6LOTO    N@HKJR
 E2  C* * *                END
      *
E1   C                     END
